    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your ability to draw upon your latent source of aether to impart effects upon your weapon is impressive.</p><p>Power weapons you wield have their damage die stepped up to d6. Additionally, as an Interact action, you can reconfigure your power weapons to deal a damage type that is different from their normal output.</p><p>Choose from @Localize[PF2E.TraitCold], @Localize[PF2E.TraitElectricity], Fire, Wind, Earth and Water damage. Your power weapons deal this type of damage until you use the action again. At 10th level, you may also choose from between @Localize[PF2E.TraitVoid] and @Localize[PF2E.TraitVitality] damage, and at 14th level you may choose @Localize[PF2E.TraitForce] damage.</p>",
